===Noun===
'''splinter'''
# A [[long]], [[sharp]] [[fragment]] of material; often [[wood]].
# A [[group]] that formed by [[split]]ting off from a larger [[membership]].

====Synonyms====
*[[shard]] (1)
*[[splinter group]] (2)

====Translations====
